{"id": "1204680429110829126", "channel_id": "1204680429110829126", "type": 0, "author_id": "710710398311202816", "author_name": "xuyu_666", "author_bot": false, "content": "如題遊戲卡在這個頁面進不去，我那帳號還沒綁刪掉怕我的遊戲紀錄消失，我該怎麼辦呢？\n題外話，載入頁面的使用者協議和資源修復鍵如圖被隱藏，公告鍵下方都有但無法顯示", "timestamp": "2024-02-07T06:49:56.180000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1204680429509017600", "filename": "received_1019515562941129.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 53678, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1204680429110829126/1204680429509017600/received_1019515562941129.jpg?ex=6a00d354&is=69ff81d4&hm=e846f403fdf7a44abe6e221ed0392142533232bfbbd2bef8e0ff61ae06cca88a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204680429110829126", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」遊戲卡住進不去..", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1181168197425172480"]}
