{"id": "1204620330480566302", "channel_id": "1204620330480566302", "type": 0, "author_id": "733514425847513171", "author_name": "xuan4185", "author_bot": false, "content": "在莉茲開大時，我手上有三張打擊、一張誘蛾、兩張死滅，其中三張打擊應該能造成(30+8)×3的狂氣回復，然而實際上殘缺面孔的效果似乎只有觸發一次", "timestamp": "2024-02-07T02:51:07.550000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1204620330807730186", "filename": "Screen_Recording_20240206_131219.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 1056232, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1204620330480566302/1204620330807730186/Screen_Recording_20240206_131219.mp4?ex=6a009b5b&is=69ff49db&hm=e8e25b2b6e64a5403912f2769ff9f609b1f35fdeeac3abd53b0de110d5118450&"}, {"id": "1204620331126620241", "filename": "Screen_Recording_20240206_131219_exported_292.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 190522, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1204620330480566302/1204620331126620241/Screen_Recording_20240206_131219_exported_292.jpg?ex=6a009b5b&is=69ff49db&hm=dae1ed2dc4017403f40b216a5f3995e6c9510cee5f0374fabab70bd61b960f88&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204620330480566302", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」殘缺面孔未正確觸發", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
